{"tid":1833164,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Cammi 新相變「12頭身」走火入魔P圖階磚直變曲","createTime":"2020-01-21T16:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T10:36:26.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b644b7ccf7c324fcf3f0c27039cfb986c87a0995","tid":1833164,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:33:44.000Z","msg":"Cammi一向對P圖好有心得，張張放上網嘅靚相都執過，P圖技巧出神入化，加上擅長擺甫士，令佢真人同上鏡真係可以完全係兩個人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2545000/2547553/82979025_10163421103620389_5522241702477168640_o_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2545000%2F2547553%2F82979025_10163421103620389_5522241702477168640_o_600.jpg&h=b0393d64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cc54b5cae2f1b0eebdf7a1a09e4f5f9c7aae251","tid":1833164,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:33:54.000Z","msg":"不過Cammi幾叻都有失手時候，日前佢上載去韓國嘅靚相，只見佢靠枱邊托住頭影相，上半身好身材超突出、腰圍很纖細，但細心看看，她身後的階磚牆明顯變形扭曲，直線變曲線，實在是P得太明顯。不過一班狂迷一於少理，繼續留言大讚偶像「漂亮迷人」、「有您就有好心情」。但同時亦都有網友發現佢P圖的痕跡，仲話佢企係方格面前影相係玩命：「修圖的技術要再練練了」、「大腿右側是有p&hellip;磁磚都變形了。」"},{"pid":"76e40f6bee7ff65e8db18894ae9c944843a76283","tid":1833164,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2545000/2547553/82660108_10163427113850389_3365333242667335680_o_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2545000%2F2547553%2F82660108_10163427113850389_3365333242667335680_o_600.jpg&h=e27bc6d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95e713f6a2f551fb2cdf1e50f35c4f180b4c1882","tid":1833164,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"去年曾經上過《東張西望》露過真樣，當時那一集是以「P圖」為主題，女主持特地帶她到街上做對比實測，不過看到Cammi真人，唔少市民完全認不出。望返Cammi平時相片上圍時大時細，雙腿亦時長時短，亦都難怪一般市民認唔到。之前Cammi接受專訪時，坦承自己係會P圖，而且至少用會兩個apps執相，又好講究每個細節，包括燈光、角度、天色、膚色等全部都會P過，處理一張相片最少就要花15分鐘。"},{"pid":"814900cdddc3a154f5b790c7bbd695e645bdb485","tid":1833164,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2545000/2547553/dds_600_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2545000%2F2547553%2Fdds_600_600.jpg&h=606aeb2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8206a3c669a1bbfa1f0083a12cb31a14ed44ce50","tid":1833164,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"事實上Cammi亦唔係第一次老貓燒鬚P圖出事，前排佢上傳新的水着靚相都嚇親網友，事關佢P出極度誇張的身材比例，上圍同頭部一樣咁大，仲有一對直到起角嘅腳，真係唔簡單！"},{"pid":"f992592d3ad26564dfb14a38cf52e27b79cead45","tid":1833164,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊位，認唔到"},{"pid":"eb4cc67b0e5705723636d57df61636a5772c171d","tid":1833164,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2545000/2547553/UjQg2NZcABm3e5AFH9lgGOVi-pJSNZZtxtHgWMbR4Fg_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2545000%2F2547553%2FUjQg2NZcABm3e5AFH9lgGOVi-pJSNZZtxtHgWMbR4Fg_600.jpg&h=4bb2af78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc4dc5d8b6cc461e393f57cb5c44330e5b191cb2","tid":183316